creator: 플랫포머스
descriptionHtml:
With Veteran, find work with ease!
“Are you still wasting days without work?”

Veteran offers reliable services that connect employment agencies and workers quickly and easily so that anyone can use them conveniently.

〔Advantages of Veteran’s services〕

-Easy management of job alerts
Veteran manages your job opportunities by receiving job offers from your employment agency beforehand and checking the job description and the location of workplaces in advance before accepting those offers.

-Easy management of schedule
Your calendar in regard to scheduled/completed work and job notifications is automatically managed on a daily and monthly basis.

-Urgently wanted job alerts
Even if you do not get a job from your employment agency, don’t worry.
Customized job notifications will be sent in real time to our members who have not received a job offer.
You can also find the jobs you want on the “job information” or “customized job” menu by region or job type, and apply for them.

-Attendance notification
Don’t worry about attendance, especially on your first day at work.
Your attendance will be notified to your employment agency at a preset time and will be automatically verified based on the GPS system.
With Veteran, be free from worries about unemployment!
 
〔Veteran website information〕

-Web designer’s homepage : http://www.platformers.co.kr

title: Veteran for workers

creator: 플랫포머스
descriptionHtml:
With Veteran, find work with ease!
“Are you still wasting days without work?”

Veteran offers reliable services that connect employment agencies and workers quickly and easily so that anyone can use them conveniently.

〔Advantages of Veteran’s services〕

-Easy management of job alerts
Veteran manages your job opportunities by receiving job offers from your employment agency beforehand and checking the job description and the location of workplaces in advance before accepting those offers.

-Easy management of schedule
Your calendar in regard to scheduled/completed work and job notifications is automatically managed on a daily and monthly basis.

-Urgently wanted job alerts
Even if you do not get a job from your employment agency, don’t worry.
Customized job notifications will be sent in real time to our members who have not received a job offer.
You can also find the jobs you want on the “job information” or “customized job” menu by region or job type, and apply for them.

-Attendance notification
Don’t worry about attendance, especially on your first day at work.
Your attendance will be notified to your employment agency at a preset time and will be automatically verified based on the GPS system.
With Veteran, be free from worries about unemployment!
